snippet.title: This Car Made My Racing Game 10x Cooler
snippet.description:
Wishlist Apex Rush on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2638250/Apex_Rush

Join the Discord Server! - https://discord.gg/XnCJXbG753

Other Apex Rush Socials: 
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/apexrush

In today's devlog we take a look at the new car, the "Alera" which has a really fun jump ability! The new customization features, stunt mode, and more!

Thank you all for the support of Apex Rush so far, excited to bring you more updates.
